Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就把白浪給帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到處找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是白浪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢 幻 泡 影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然什麼都沒說就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人 我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參見役之行者的孫女螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了 螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紋章僅授予能夠傳承禁術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真是白浪大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如此吃驚也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是從鳴人那聽說了事情的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是白浪大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好謝謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了句「之後就拜託你了」 便離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽鳴人說 你想復興家族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真心的話 能夠聽一下我的建議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遁兵衛還健在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他想通過分離之術埋葬禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識遁兵衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起修行過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不同意遁兵衛的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父波濤曾受役之行者大人之命保護禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親是一直守護禁術和土蜘蛛一族榮耀的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被盯上禁術的人殺死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以父親的死為契機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役之行者大人將禁術轉移到了葛城山要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓我從村中逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一日 會為土蜘蛛一族重返
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親被殺 我不得不逃出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我們父子是掌握禁術的唯一倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也有著同樣的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和螢小姐合力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能復活禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不用埋葬它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復興土蜘蛛一族也是我的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起實現父親和役之行者的夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過這座山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要塞的周邊已經大致搜查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人找到白浪的事明明已經告訴她了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著詩形出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先中止儀式的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先搜索螢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能多放出一些搜索用的老鼠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.超獸偽畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫給遁兵衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要聯繫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要跟詩形大人說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你肆意妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為早就割捨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼此刻我仍對師父的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是查克拉操縱的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信鴿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢發來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和白浪大人同以復興土蜘蛛一族為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的種種非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟子螢 敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到白浪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我也解放了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道白浪被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不折不扣的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還在擔心白浪老大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你和禁術丫頭見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的計劃就泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個結界是老大特製的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能奪取對方查克拉的經典之作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這結界中還能反抗的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照老大的作戰 使用下一個術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重.夢幻泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就解不開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西沒什麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到被剝奪了這麼多查克拉竟然還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是佩服他的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的事 我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到匪首竟然是白浪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把螢帶到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大應該到村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也撤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土蜘蛛一族的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎 螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 出來吧 螢小姐回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的人這是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是略施小術讓他們聽話一些罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了得到禁術這個寶貝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪大人 你騙了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要補充的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了保護禁術的老爸的人正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了搶走禁術而殺了老爸 螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經在我的控制中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得到禁術了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是枯枝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其這麼沒效率地搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如用多重影分身來得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想毀掉螢被帶走的重要線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有如此體重的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是帶著一個人奔跑時留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從留下的痕跡中搜索是忍者最基本的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和螢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張口閉口師傅 看來並沒有好好修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為執著於師父這種無聊的事才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從好色仙人那裡學到了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體術和忍術就不說了 還有非常厲害的術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他並不只是嚴格要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為忍者而言 最重要的是不放棄的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是從師父那裡得到了最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有師父吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和師父一起的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂忍者 就要迅速完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是追蹤被奪走的卷軸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你搶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的可是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要糟蹋生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣脫逃不配做忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可為而為之也不能算是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為自己對師父很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股力量 是超越你器量的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的並不是我 而是我體內的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把我看成了容器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 劍所言屬實的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這不是土蜘蛛一族的村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是痕跡一直延續到了這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢在這個村子遭到了賊匪們的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的人並不歡迎螢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 禁術是令人忌諱的存在 這很好理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上螢在此被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能賊匪和村民相互勾結 又或許是村民視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這個村子就像賊匪們的據點一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 留下的腳印也相當不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是得到禁術和螢之後大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是打算引我們上鉤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止 追蹤過於順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的追蹤反而值得懷疑 我從師父那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也從師父那學到不少東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救回螢之後 也分享一些給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為謝禮 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們要和賊匪聯手對付我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎被操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒法不傷害村民繼續前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的氣勢哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狼狽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們把村民給…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手 別給他們喘息的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨行動也該適可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你們為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在尋找從葛城山失蹤的螢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是體力勞動型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然耗費了這麼多查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 兵糧丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這種話 萬一發生什麼事怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我特製的兵糧丸 一定要恢復精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個非常難吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光石火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你們妨礙老大的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火縛之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗費了那麼多時間辛苦去做準備也算是得到回報了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從禁術中被解放 你也應該相當激動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木遁之術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我們 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救螢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來救你 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說前面的查克拉在不斷聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然界的查克拉正朝著同一方向流去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿被某處吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢恐怕就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白浪那傢伙到底想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態刻不容緩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有動嘴的時間不如加快腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術發動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢 我們這就到了
